                <head>65. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On February 20, the 13th regular session of the <gloss target="#t_UN1"
                        >U.N</gloss>. General Assembly resumed to consider the future of the Trust
                    Territories of the Cameroons under French administration and the Cameroons under
                    British administration. For the verbatim records of the resumed session, which
                    lasted through March 13, see U.N. docs. <gloss target="#t_A1"
                    >A</gloss>/PV.793–794.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
